Id":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"95f1dfa9ad","type":"paragraph","text":"12月23日","index":98,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"bca768bb50","type":"paragraph","text":"军管小组传达中央关于公安机关实行军管的决定。","index":99,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"72b0ef8f80","type":"paragraph","text":"12月25日","index":100,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"28f38bf981","type":"paragraph","text":"几天来，“兵团”组织处级以上干部，揭发厅党组的问题。即所谓“揭发黑党组阶级斗争的盖子”。","index":101,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"a073540062","type":"paragraph","text":"12月30日","index":102,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"aa9e4451ef","type":"paragraph","text":"“兵团”又开大会，进一步揭批厅党组。","index":103,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"359968688d","type":"paragraph","text":"4月29日","index":104,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"fa9f30842c","type":"paragraph","text":"二、五、八处对钟枫采取抄家行动。","index":105,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"b6f09e2ec1","type":"paragraph","text":"夜12时，厅内有一百多人强行夺取集中保管的枪支。","index":106,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"f8056a75d7","type":"paragraph","text":"4月30日","index":107,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"0eeb21d70d","type":"paragraph","text":"“公安兵团”发出“勒令”，钟枫被撵出原住宿舍，并组织6人严管。","index":108,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"9ffad64c45","type":"paragraph","text":"5月17日","index":109,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"4ff087acae","type":"paragraph","text":"全厅批斗钟枫大会（在保育院）。军管后，“公安兵团领导成员”改为“运动服务组”。大会由运动服务组陈勇主持。","index":110,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"3747c0b523","type":"paragraph","text":"5月19日","index":111,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"9c2e164863","type":"paragraph","text":"在八处办公室批斗钟枫。参加批斗的有二、五、八三个处的兵团服务员：黄经孟、刘祉高、李永和、唐毓殷、罗珠含、韦家庆、黄子燧、黄理直、易子仪、兰日廉、陈天华等。","index":112,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"f7ce6988c0","type":"paragraph","text":"5月20日","index":113,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"87941122b1","type":"paragraph","text":"在八处办公室继续批斗钟枫，仍以二、五、八三个处为主，其他处派代表参加。在这两次的批斗中少数极端分子大打出手，钟枫遭到残酷迫害。","index":114,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"eeced18dd3","type":"paragraph","text":"5月23日","index":115,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"e5c830388f","type":"paragraph","text":"下午，召开全厅批斗钟枫大会，陈勇主持大会。挂牌陪斗的有：鲁源、常明宇、兰秀芳、刘蔚芝、梁正、王冠玉、兰威、韦君毅、张晖、甄杰、陈国、李健、李敬民、杨学池，还有检察院的芦秀生等。在这次大会中，少数人残酷迫害老同志，军管会当众逮捕了李敬民，会后还进行了游斗。","index":116,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"2f8a35b75f","type":"paragraph","text":"5月24日","index":117,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"79ea236785","type":"paragraph","text":"下午继续批斗钟枫。挂牌陪斗的除了昨天的以外，还增加了韦立仁、谷亘华、单连喜、李乐群、胡炳松等。批斗结束时，宣布：1、钟枫全家8人，每人每月只发给生活费15元；2、把鲁源赶出厅长宿舍；3、所有陪斗的都进行监督劳动。军管组戴福庆最后讲了话。","index":118,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"6b8b40e95c","type":"paragraph","text":"5月25日","index":119,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"a5c257750b","type":"paragraph","text":"二、五、八处发表联战公报，内容：批斗钟枫实况之一、二、三、四。二处连夜突击出版大批判专栏诬蔑钟枫是“国民党的官，顽固的走资派”，还有5幅漫画。","index":120,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"d9a381633d","type":"paragraph","text":"至5月底，由王世桂等人组织全厅干部，以及劳改场干部连续在本厅和茅桥礼堂，批斗王冠玉等，会上发生残酷打人情况。很多同志遭到严重摧残。","index":121,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"e096d19bc6","type":"paragraph","text":"6月1日","index":122,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"295928fc12","type":"paragraph","text":"“林业厅事件”于5月30日发生，武斗急骤升级，“公安兵团”紧张备战，今天开始全体集中睡觉。","index":123,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"40622671d5","type":"paragraph","text":"6月8日","index":124,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"03242f9d59","type":"paragraph","text":"“兵团”开大会，宣布：1、王农必须在10日以前回来；2、再发一次电报给金立诚，如果不回就扣工资或开除；3、李明清私带机密文件，今晚必须交回；4、“勒令”丘栋霖检讨。","index":125,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"6e0203e3cd","type":"paragraph","text":"6月11日","index":126,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"68a853f162","type":"paragraph","text":"上午，再次组织厅内所谓“走资派”、“叛徒”、“反革命两面派”等进行游斗。","index":127,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"1768683f9c","type":"paragraph","text":"6月27日","index":128,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"6b438899de","type":"paragraph","text":"军管会宣布：从6月份起停发王农、江毓珍、金立诚、李明清等的工资。限庞举清、雷敬余、杜裘等6月底回厅。","index":129,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"8e9c592880","type":"paragraph","text":"7月5日","index":130,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"0e39e46fa3","type":"paragraph","text":"二、五、八处“批斗钟枫小组”整天批斗钟枫。追查钟枫的家庭、历史、入党、入伍等情况。","index":131,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"190bba2eb1","type":"paragraph","text":"7月6日","index":132,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"ce06e0bdf6","type":"paragraph","text":"“七·三”布告今天公布。","index":133,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"3d728aaeeb","type":"paragraph","text":"“公安厅兵团”再次掀起揪斗“小爬虫”的高潮。","index":134,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"6731bf4062","type":"paragraph","text":"下午，揪斗了钟枫及“走资派”、“叛徒”和“小爬虫”。被诬为“小爬虫”的有：赵文祥、于有智、覃彦华、王彦生、黄淑暹、底书贵等。游斗中，一些极端分子再次大打出手。","index":135,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"4a92d2e9a5","type":"paragraph","text":"7月15日","index":136,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"a7f53702fa","type":"paragraph","text":"办公室王嘉祥被冯俊卿等人灌大便。","index":137,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"bfd813becd","type":"paragraph","text":"陈天华、高志才等带领数十人，跳围墙前往参加攻打百货大楼。","index":138,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"1be3bedecb","type":"paragraph","text":"7月18日","index":139,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"18f44e3a3d"},{"id":"30c118982a","type":"paragraph","text":"全厅召开坚决贯彻“七·三”布告誓师大会。组织一百多人前往百货大楼、明园、解放路等地参加